{"word":"G652 - ἀπόστολος - apóstolos - ap-os'-tol-os - Apostle","slug":"G652","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπόστολος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apóstolos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-os'-tol-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apostle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C2; - apostolos</b> - <i>ap-os'-tol-os</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G649\">G649</a>; a <i>delegate</i>; specifically an <i>ambassador</i> of the Gospel; officially a <i>commissioner</i> of Christ (&ldquo;apostle&rdquo;), (with miraculous powers): - apostle, messenger, he that is sent."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1821\">G1821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3992\">G3992</a>, <a href=\"#/G5570\">G5570</a>, <a href=\"#/G649\">G649</a>, <a href=\"#/G651\">G651</a>"}]}